<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190205>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 14. Chaetotaxy of posterior part of Abd. IV, V and VI: 13, F. culter sp. nov.; 14, F. k u r u s h i c a (Russia: E Caucasus)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190205/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190202>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. F. culter sp. nov.: 1, Habitus and chaetotaxy (macrochaetae of Abd. V and VI not shown); 2, Th. III; 3, Abd. IV – VI." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190202/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190203>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 – 8. F. c u lt er sp. nov.: 4, anterior part of head; 5, posterior chaetotaxy of manubrium (laterobasal setae pointed); 6 – 8, furca, different views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190203/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190204>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 12. Chaetotaxy of posterior part of Abd. IV, V and VI in four species of fimetaria - group: 9, F. sparsosetosa (Russia: SW Siberia); 10, F. b i s e t o s a. (Russia: Novaya Zemlya Archipelago); 11, F. litsteri (W Ukraine); 12, F. fimetaria (Russia: Caucasus)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190204/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

